Gilbert.

557
00:44:31,560 --> 00:44:33,551
Uh-huh. Okay.

558
00:44:33,640 --> 00:44:35,870
Let me in on where
you do your hiring.

559
00:44:36,000 --> 00:44:38,195
Hi.

560
00:44:38,280 --> 00:44:41,078
Shh!
He's out cold.

561
00:44:42,400 --> 00:44:45,278
