568
00:45:03,760 --> 00:45:05,557
- Yeah?
- Yeah.

569
00:45:05,680 --> 00:45:07,796
Oh... do you think,

570
00:45:07,920 --> 00:45:10,673
do you think Marlene
would want to help out?

571
00:45:10,800 --> 00:45:14,679
