574
00:45:21,440 --> 00:45:23,908
l wouldn't want her to
think l was competitive.

575
00:45:24,000 --> 00:45:26,958
You know?
About Claire's friendship.

576
00:45:27,040 --> 00:45:30,191
You understand Marlene
pretty well already.

577
00:45:37,680 --> 00:45:41,229
Well, good...
so l'll be going.

578
00:45:41,320 --> 00:45:45,711
Okay, good.
l'm real glad you came by.

579
00:45:49,120 --> 00:45:50,951
- Bye.
- Bye.

