because l didn't protect her.

683
00:56:11,640 --> 00:56:14,996
l don't think so,
Claire.

684
00:56:26,920 --> 00:56:29,673
Shh.

685
00:56:29,760 --> 00:56:33,230
Marlene wants to get together tonight
to make out a guest list.

686
00:56:33,360 --> 00:56:35,590
l'm not sure this party
is a good idea now.

687
00:56:35,680 --> 00:56:37,750
- What do you think?
- l think we should go ahead with it.

688
00:56:37,880 --> 00:56:40,474
Everyone could use
some cheering up,

689
00:56:40,600 --> 00:56:44,275
especially Claire. You know how
she's been blaming herself.

690
00:56:44,400 --> 00:56:48,279
Yeah, l think
you're right.

691
00:56:48,400 --> 00:56:50,231
Guess l just
needed to hear it.

692
00:56:52,240 --> 00:56:54,754
[ Cooing ]

693
00:56:54,880 --> 00:56:56,711
[ Marlene ]
Thanks for lunch.

694
00:56:56,800 --> 00:56:58,756
l especially liked the part where
we picked up the fertilizer.

695
00:56:58,880 --> 00:57:00,791
- Oh, you liked that?
- Oh, yeah.

696
00:57:00,920 --> 00:57:03,070
[ Peyton ]
Hi, you two.

697
00:57:03,200 --> 00:57:05,350
- Hi. Oh, can l take him?
- Oh, sure.

698
00:57:05,440 --> 00:57:09,956
- Hi, sweetheart. Hello.
- [ Crying ]

699
00:57:10,080 --> 00:57:11,911
- Let me help.
