every time l see him.

701
00:57:15,080 --> 00:57:16,433
[ Crying ]

702
00:57:16,560 --> 00:57:19,870
[ Marlene ] He's got a great
set of lungs, doesn't he?

703
00:57:20,000 --> 00:57:22,753
- Oh, what's the matter?
- You want mommy?

704
00:57:22,880 --> 00:57:24,757
You want to go?

705
00:57:24,840 --> 00:57:28,913
- What happened, ohhh?
- [ Crying ]

706
00:57:31,560 --> 00:57:33,391
Shh.

707
00:57:33,520 --> 00:57:36,318
l don't know what got into
him today. Want me to try?

708
00:57:36,440 --> 00:57:39,477
- Wanna go to Peyton?
- Ah, it's okay.

709
00:57:39,560 --> 00:57:41,551
Yeah.

710
00:57:41,640 --> 00:57:44,473
Yeah, it's okay,
little one.

711
00:57:47,360 --> 00:57:49,635
[ Chiming ]

712
00:57:49,760 --> 00:57:53,070
What is that
annoying noise?

713
00:57:56,000 --> 00:57:58,992
Wind chimes. lt was a gift
